OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThree warnings before boy, 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F6, shot teacher - lawyer   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, On the day a six-year-old pupil shot   
OL,6, and wounded his teacher in the US state
OL,7, of Virginia, school leaders were warned
OL,8, three times that the boy might have a  
OL,9, gun, a lawyer for the teacher said.    
OL,11,FThis included a request to search the  
OL,12,Fboy and a report from another child who
OL,13,Fsaid the boy had shown him a gun.      
OL,15,FThe teacher - Abigail Zwerner, 25 - is 
OL,16,Frecovering after being released from   
OL,17,Fhospital last week.                    
OL,19,FIn the fallout, the school's           
OL,20,Fsuperintendent has now lost his job.   
